00:16:33,701 --> 00:16:34,909
- Oh, Marilyn, there you are.

378
00:16:35,035 --> 00:16:36,786
- Carolyn, happy holidays.

379
00:16:36,912 --> 00:16:38,413
- Oh, I have something for you
in the den.

380
00:16:38,539 --> 00:16:39,580
It's marked.
