381
00:16:39,707 --> 00:16:41,040
So before you go.

382
00:16:41,166 --> 00:16:42,166
- Thank you, Carolyn.

383
00:16:42,292 --> 00:16:44,210
- Hello, I'm Carolyn Soule,

384
00:16:44,336 --> 00:16:45,378
Jack Woolf's wife.

385
00:16:45,504 --> 00:16:46,754
- This is Emilia Greenleaf.

