00:51:49,898 --> 00:51:53,526
- You don't understand.

1130
00:51:53,652 --> 00:51:55,986
You don't understand
about Collegiate or anything.

1131
00:51:56,113 --> 00:51:57,363
You're from New Rochelle.

1132
00:51:57,489 --> 00:51:59,782
