00:52:21,096 --> 00:52:22,263
- You don't have to.

1143
00:52:22,389 --> 00:52:26,267
- Only if I can let go
of the wall.

1144
00:52:26,393 --> 00:52:28,018
- Right on.

1145
00:52:28,145 --> 00:52:29,353
One more try.

1146
00:52:58,717 --> 00:52:59,842
- This is done?

