1176
00:53:56,858 --> 00:53:58,901
I can be a kid,
and Emilia can be a mom.

1177
00:53:59,027 --> 00:54:01,403
- And it was my favorite book
too when I was your age,

1178
00:54:01,529 --> 00:54:02,863
which is pretty weird.

