00:54:06,618 --> 00:54:09,662
- Well, Will wanted
a real stir-fry, not takeout.

1182
00:54:09,788 --> 00:54:10,829
- Mm-hmm.
- Jump in.

1183
00:54:10,956 --> 00:54:11,956
- Sure.

